that hasn't been said already.

26:42.010 --> 26:45.013
Big mistake. Big fucking mistake.

26:55.690 --> 26:58.568
[Olivia] There are limits to what
we can do to help another person,

26:59.320 --> 27:01.311
no matter how much we wish there weren't.

27:01.990 --> 27:04.026
