that she may have known

29:25.180 --> 29:27.637
or might have been in distress?

29:31.470 --> 29:33.097
[Olivia sobbing]

29:39.020 --> 29:40.351
[shop door opening]

29:45.610 --> 29:48.352
-Hey, Mom.
